::Zardus::

Zardus looks from Nemesis to Delta.

"Allright. A new craft has landed. We're going to check it out. Panzertron, 
the bot I have made contact with has requested that I come alone. You two 
will accompany as 'ghosts'. There are a few portable cloaking devices in the 
weapon storage. You'll both stay cloaked. If he decides to attack, we'll at 
least be able to defend ourselves."
